<item>
            <title>[LU-11394] Updates for ZFS 0.8.0, no separate SPL</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11394</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Beginning in ZFS 0.8.0, SPL will no longer be a seperate package.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lbuild&lt;/tt&gt; needs to be updated to account for this.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;build m4 scripts (&lt;tt&gt;config/lustre-build-zfs.m4&lt;/tt&gt;) need to be updated&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;man pages mkfs.lustre(8) and tunefs.lustre(8) need to be updated&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;dkms package needs to be updated&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Debian build needs to be updated&lt;/p&gt;</description>
